// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1887 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: eb6a1a30-2abf-5f22-a845-8113ed6fcf51

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.04*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
